title: Phone Bazzar
describe: Features  Second-hand mobile bazaar. You can buy or sell your Second-hand phones.  Have three roles, Admin, sellers, and buyer. seller or buyer is a public role.  Buyer can choose and buy any products. Sellers can add and sell his/her products. Used Technology : React.js, Tailwind, Firebase, Vercel, Node.js, Express.js, Daisy Ui, MongoDB, React Hook Form, Axios, React Query,
